msgstr "Glavno okno Karbon"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.calligra.metainfo.xml:87
msgid "This release add flatpak support to the Calligra Office suite."
msgstr "Ta izdaja dodaja podporo za flatpak v paket Calligra Office."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.calligra.metainfo.xml:93
msgid ""
"The most significant changes are that Calligra has been fully transitioned "
"to Qt6 and KF6, along with a major overhaul of its user interface."
msgstr ""
"Najpomembnejše spremembe so, da je bila Calligra v celoti preusmerjena na "
"Qt6 in KF6, skupaj z obsežno prenovo uporabniškega vmesnika."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.calligra.metainfo.xml:94
msgid ""
"Words, Sheets, and Stage now feature a new sidebar design. The “Custom "
"Shape” docker has been removed, and custom shapes are now accessible through "
"a popup menu in the toolbar across all Calligra applications. We simplified "
"the toolbar and removed the basic copy, paste and cut actions."
msgstr ""
"Words, Sheets in Stage imajo zdaj novo zasnovo stranske vrstice. Priklopno "
"okno »Oblika po meri« je bilo odstranjeno, oblike po meri pa so zdaj "
"dostopne prek pojavnega menija v orodni vrstici v vseh aplikacijah Calligra. "
"Orodno vrstico smo poenostavili in odstranili osnovna dejanja kopiranja, "
"lepljenja in izrezovanja."
